      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms Juicer produces .hic files from raw sequence data, but does not mention ENCODE uniform processing pipeline, ENCODE reference format, checksum verification, or FASTQ-specific processing. The research question conflates Juicer (which the paper describes) with an ENCODE-specific pipeline (not mentioned in passages).",
