      "asbval:note": "No tool named 'juicer_cli_tools' appears in paper. Paper describes Juicer as a unified pipeline with integrated algorithms (HiCCUPS, Arrowhead, APA) but does not name a separate 'juicer_cli_tools' package. The command-line execution is part of Juicer itself.",
